	max({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"EU*"}>} Uptake1st_ALL_Cumul) ,
    max({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"EU*"}>} Uptake2nd_ALL_Cumul) ,
)*1.1

=pick(match(v_ViewUptake, 'FIRST', 'SECOND'),

    max({<[Member State]=, [MemberState_]=-{"EU*"}>} Uptake2nd_ALL_Cumul) ,
